SYSTEM-
REQUIREMENTS:   * ECS or AGA
		* min. 1 MB ChipRam
		* min. 68020/25 Mhz
		* medplayer.library

The program switch off the multitasking. So avoid working other
programs in background.

PREFS: Copy the medplayer.library into LIBS:
       Copy the Font (XEN.font & Directory XEN) into FONTS:
       Voila!

MENU: Use the joystick in port 1 to control the menu.
      To change the number of rounds (1-99), move the pointer over
      the number, hold firebutton and press up or down.

THE GAME: In the gridfield are some bonus pieces. The collect will
          activate one of the following effects:


       SPEED - Double Speed.

       SCORE - 40 points.

       TELEPORT - Transfer the tron-bike to another random place
                  in the field.

       MIRROR-CONTROL - Change the stick-control!!
                        Left <--> Right
                        Up   <--> Down

                        The collect of a second MIRROR-CONTROL will
                        re-change it.

       HOLE - Generates a black hole somewhere in the field.
              Warning! A trip in a black hole is injurious to health!
              This hole contains ca. -900000000 kilogram
              anti-matter and 75 litre black paint. :)

       LINEBREAKER - Incease linebreaker by one.

The linebreaker allows to break through or to move over ONE own or
opponent wall. But a linebreaker allows NOT to break the flashing
deathline!

SPIELENDE: The round end, when one bike crashes and the player has
           no linebreaker over.

           After the last round, the computer will multiplicity
           the collected points and the number of wins.
           final score determines about victory and defeat.

           Only the winner can enter the Hi-Score, if possible.
